'''Burundi''', chang-sṳt miàng-chhṳ̂n '''Burundi Khiung-fò-koet''' ([[Kirundi-ngî]]: Republika y'Uburundi; [[Fap-ngî]]: République du Burundi, [byˈʁyndi]), he yit-ke vi-yî tûng-phu [[Fî-chû]] ke séu-hîn nui-liu̍k [[koet-kâ]], khì [[pet]], [[tûng]], [[sî]]-mien fûn-phe̍t vì [[Rwanda]], [[Tanzania]] lâu [[Congo Mìn-chú Khiung-fò-koet|Congo]] só pâu vì, khì-chûng lâu [[Congo Mìn-chú Khiung-fò-koet]] ke piên-kie yû chhêu-ko yit pan he chho-lo̍k chhai chho̍k-miàng ke [[Tanganyika Fù]] (Lake Tanganyika) fù mien sông.

